XFS Tools (Focus on RHEL/CentOS)

[*] xfsdump
- Used to take backup of XFS file systems
- $ xfsdump -f /tmp/backuppath /boot/important-files

[*] xfsrestore
- Used to restore backup created by xfsdump
- $ xfsrestore -f /tmp/backuppath /restore/location

[*] xfs_info
- Shows info about mounted XFS file system
- $ xfs_info /dev/sda1

[*] xfs_repair
- $ xfs_repair /dev/sda1
